==English==

===Etymology===
{{blend|trust fund|Rastafarian}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A young person with the fashion sensibilities of a [[hippie]] who subscribes to an unemployed, shiftless life of [[hedonism]] based upon an unlimited amount of funds (a trust fund).

